ne]]\n<BR>[[Alborosie]]\n<BR>1000mods\n|valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" width=200|\n'''[[Lana Del Rey]]'''\n<BR>[[Echo & the Bunnymen]]\n<BR>[[The Subways]]\n<BR>Gautier\n|valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" width=200|\n'''[[Dead Can Dance]]'''\n<BR>Monophonics\n<BR>Craig Walker\n<BR>Opera Chaotique\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n| colspan=\"4\" align=\"center\" | '''Vibe Stage'''\n|-\n!Saturday 6 July\n!Sunday 7 July \n!Monday 8 July \n!Tuesday 9 July\n|-\n|valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" width=200|\n'''Giannis Aggelakas'''\n<BR>Ypogeia Revmata & Thanos Nestopoulos\n<BR>Eirini Skulakaki\n|valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" width=200|\n'''[[Saxon (band)|Saxon]]'''\n<BR>[[Kreator]]\n<BR>[[Carcass (band)|Carcass]]\n<BR>Descending\n<BR>Endsight\n|valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" width=200|\n'''[[Iced Earth]]'''\n<BR>[[Suicidal Tendencies]]\n<BR>[[At the Gates]]\n<BR>Psycho Choke\n<BR>Black Hat Bones\n|valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" width=200|\n'''[[Septic Flesh]]'''\n<BR>[[Chaostar]]\n<BR>Acid Death\n<BR>Tardive Dyskinesia\n<BR>Mahakala\n|}\n\n==2012 lineup==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Saturday 30 June\n!Sunday 1 July\n!Monday 2 July\n|-\n|valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" width=200|\n'''[[The Locos (band)|The Locos]]'''\n<BR>[[The Last Drive]]\n<BR>[[Nashville Pussy]]\n<BR>[[Nightstalker (band)|Nightstalker]]\n<BR>Mamma Kin\n|valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" width=200|\n'''[[Ozzy Osbourne]]'''\n<BR>[[Machine Head (band)|Machine Head]]\n<BR>[[Paradise Lost (band)|Paradise Lost]]\n<BR>[[Unisonic (band)|Unisonic]]\n<BR>Planet of Zeus\n<BR>Lucky Funeral\n|valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" width=200|\n'''[[The Prodigy]]'''\n<BR>[[Iggy and the Stooges]]\n<BR>[[Everlast (musician)|Everlast]]\n<BR>GAD.\n<BR>Monovine\n|}\n\n==2011 lineup==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n| colspan=\"3\" align=\"center\" | '''Terra Stage'''\n|-\n!Friday 1 July\n!Saturday 2 July\n!Sunday 3 July\n|-\n|valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" width=200|\n'''[[Editors]]'''\n<BR>[[Cake (band)|Cake]]\n<BR>[[The Stranglers]]\